Class CSVUtilsController

java.lang.Object
controllers.CSVUtilsController
All Implemented Interfaces:
CSVUtilsInterface
public class CSVUtilsController extends Object implements CSVUtilsInterface
Controller class implementing CSVUtilsInterface for managing CSV data storage and retrieval for users, staff, patients, and medicines in the Hospital Management System.

      public ArrayList<Patient> PatientDataInit(String filePath, ArrayList<Patient> patientList)
      Initializes a list of Patient objects by reading data from a CSV file. The method processes each line, creates a new Patient for each entry, and sets additional properties like date of birth, gender, blood type, email, and phone number.
      Specified by:
      PatientDataInit in interface CSVUtilsInterface
      Parameters:
      filePath - the path to the CSV file containing patient data.
      patientList - the list to which the new Patient objects will be added.
      Returns:
      the updated ArrayList of Patient objects.

      public Boolean CheckPatientApptDoctorCSV(String filePath, String patientID, String doctorID)

      Specified by:
      CheckPatientApptDoctorCSV in interface CSVUtilsInterface
      Parameters:
